The paper proposes a deep learning model for top-N recommendation with side information. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and specifically, the sub-categories of information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and computer vision (cs.CV) may be relevant as side information can come in various forms such as text, images, or metadata.
